1. OPEN THE WEBSITE
   - Open index.html in your browser
   - Or host on a web server

2. INSTALL AS APP:
   On Desktop (Chrome/Edge):
   - Look for the "Install" button on the page
   - Or click the install button next to the book mark star in the address bar
   - Follow the installation prompts

3. OFFLINE USAGE:
   - Once installed, the app works offline
   - Your music stays on your device
   - No internet required after first visit

4. TROUBLESHOOTING:
   - Make sure all files are in the same folder
   - Icons must be in "icons/" folder
   - Use HTTPS for full PWA features
   - Clear browser cache if icons don't appear